vante Rechtsprechung europäischer Gerichtshöfe in die Sammlung einbezogen.  aThis collection on general religious law and the relationship between church and state is provided by the judiciary of state courts. It is the only one of its kind in the German-speaking world. Since volume 39, the collection has included judgments made by European courts that are relevant to the situation in Germany.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 07. Nov 2022) 4aEntscheidungssammlung. 4aKirchenrecht. 7aLAW / Public.2bisacsh  aChurch law.  alaw reports.1 aBaldus, Manfred, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMuckel, Stefan, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2022z9783110993011oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz97831107362430 cprintz978311073956540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311073618240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110736182423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110736182/original  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGCb2022  aZDB-23-DGGb2022